Jadi,

00:34:18.880 --> 00:34:20.880
Cikgu Cheng sepatutnya yang pergi.

00:34:21.800 --> 00:34:22.260
Tolonglah.

00:34:24.190 --> 00:34:25.250
Saya akan pergi segera.

00:34:45.480 --> 00:34:47.320
Saya Cheng Yunpao dari Pulau Camellia,

00:34:47.320 --> 00:34:49.920
cawangan
Central Plains Sword Alliance.

00:34:50.070 --> 00:34:51.870
Salam, Penghulu Istana Wanyu.

00:34:52.820 --> 00:34:53.480
Mengapa Perikatan Pedang Dataran Tengah

00:34:53.480 --> 00:34:54.840
Mengunjungi Istana Biluo?

